  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289900/extras/4233a6d8f3deaa36d7443000596790fe.poster.avif?t=1588921040\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289900/extras/4233a6d8f3deaa36d7443000596790fe.webm?t=1588921040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289900/extras/4233a6d8f3deaa36d7443000596790fe.mp4?t=1588921040\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Deck building card battle \"NoWaitHero\"<br>There is no need to wait during a duel.<br>Seize the victory ahead of the choice.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289900/extras/b9773fb004deea8741c1884d00755a4d.poster.avif?t=1588921040\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289900/extras/b9773fb004deea8741c1884d00755a4d.webm?t=1588921040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289900/extras/b9773fb004deea8741c1884d00755a4d.mp4?t=1588921040\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>In this game, you don't have to wait for the enemy to act.<br>They act at the same time as each other. There is no need to wait for the other party.<br>The enemy's movements are predictable, so let's get ahead of them.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289900/extras/0db3b55fea205ec7c380be9119b13c47.poster.avif?t=1588921040\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289900/extras/0db3b55fea205ec7c380be9119b13c47.webm?t=1588921040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289900/extras/0db3b55fea205ec7c380be9119b13c47.mp4?t=1588921040\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You can get new cards by defeating enemies.<br>Cards are stacked and only the top card can be used.<br>The choice you make will make a big difference in the battle.　<br>Build up your cards and experience to take on more formidable enemies.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289900/extras/6173ff66754022e772407fd1aa9d29a8.poster.avif?t=1588921040\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289900/extras/6173ff66754022e772407fd1aa9d29a8.webm?t=1588921040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289900/extras/6173ff66754022e772407fd1aa9d29a8.mp4?t=1588921040\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The card has restrictions on use.<br>If you use it crudely, you'll be pushed into a corner.<br>The enemy is also a hero.<br>Use it all to your advantage and win in style!</li></ul><br>You are the one who will defeat all the heroes and win the Hero Royal.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289900/extras/4233a6d8f3deaa36d7443000596790fe.poster.avif?t=1588921040\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289900/extras/4233a6d8f3deaa36d7443000596790fe.webm?t=1588921040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289900/extras/4233a6d8f3deaa36d7443000596790fe.mp4?t=1588921040\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Deck building card battle \"NoWaitHero\"<br>There is no need to wait during a duel.<br>Seize the victory ahead of the choice.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289900/extras/b9773fb004deea8741c1884d00755a4d.poster.avif?t=1588921040\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289900/extras/b9773fb004deea8741c1884d00755a4d.webm?t=1588921040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289900/extras/b9773fb004deea8741c1884d00755a4d.mp4?t=1588921040\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>In this game, you don't have to wait for the enemy to act.<br>They act at the same time as each other. There is no need to wait for the other party.<br>The enemy's movements are predictable, so let's get ahead of them.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289900/extras/0db3b55fea205ec7c380be9119b13c47.poster.avif?t=1588921040\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289900/extras/0db3b55fea205ec7c380be9119b13c47.webm?t=1588921040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289900/extras/0db3b55fea205ec7c380be9119b13c47.mp4?t=1588921040\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You can get new cards by defeating enemies.<br>Cards are stacked and only the top card can be used.<br>The choice you make will make a big difference in the battle.　<br>Build up your cards and experience to take on more formidable enemies.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289900/extras/6173ff66754022e772407fd1aa9d29a8.poster.avif?t=1588921040\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289900/extras/6173ff66754022e772407fd1aa9d29a8.webm?t=1588921040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289900/extras/6173ff66754022e772407fd1aa9d29a8.mp4?t=1588921040\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The card has restrictions on use.<br>If you use it crudely, you'll be pushed into a corner.<br>The enemy is also a hero.<br>Use it all to your advantage and win in style!</li></ul><br>You are the one who will defeat all the heroes and win the Hero Royal.",
